    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n      <strong>Psionic Discipline:</strong>&nbsp;psychometabolism;\n    <br>\n    <strong>Level:</strong>&nbsp;Psion/Wilder 1, Psychic Warrior 1;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    <br>\n    \n    <strong>Power Display:</strong>&nbsp;Material and olfactory<br>\n      <strong>Manifesting Time:</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Range:</strong>&nbsp;touch<br>\n    \n    <strong>Target:</strong>&nbsp;you<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration:</strong>&nbsp;1 min./level<br>\n    <strong>Power Points/Spell Points Cost:</strong>&nbsp;1<br>\n        <strong>Saving Throw:</strong>&nbsp;none\n        <br>\n        <strong>Power Resistance:</strong>&nbsp;no<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  \n\n<p>You suffuse yourself with power, gaining 5 temporary hit points. Using this power again when an earlier manifestation has not expired merely replaces the older temporary hit points (if any remain) with the newer ones.\n</p><p><b>Augment:</b> For every additional power point you spend, the number of temporary hit points you gain increases by 5.\n</p>\n<hr/>\n\n\n\n</div>\n",
